  "statement": {
    "ambiguity_status": "minor",
    "intended": "Let $h(n)$ be minimal such that every graph on $n$ vertices where every set of $7$ vertices contains a triangle (a copy of $K_3$) must contain a clique on at least $h(n)$ vertices. Estimate $h(n)$ - in particular, do there exist constants $c_1,c_2>0$ such that\\[n^{1/3+c_1}\\ll h(n) \\ll n^{1/2-c_2}?\\]",
